song.title: Hip-Hop Lullaby
song.info: Again a tune that looks like some fairy-tale music. Some jazzy breaks in the middle, some hip-hop drums and very, very high quality instruments (99% of sounds are 16bit). Melody may seem a little "cheesy" but I like it anyway. It's a pity that good sounds make it bigger. Btw, the song was written in four days, and I spent around 20 hours making it.
